{
  "id": "4-3",
  "title": "Act 3: Victory",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch4_act3_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "Elias, now.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Elias's fingers were already jacked into the building's main signal conduit. He sat in the corner of the hall on the floor, his back against the wall, pain throbbing from the wound on his back. His neural synchronization rate was low enough that he didn't dare look at it.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "But his consciousness was still clear. That was enough.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Shield control core accessing……",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> External verification barriers ── bypassed",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Final encryption layer ── cracking in progress",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "In the hall, Alea fought to hold the line with Soren and Lyra.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The soldier count diminished from twelve to eight, then from eight to five—not because they had defeated them, but because some received higher-priority redeployment orders and were reassigned to lock down the building's exterior exits.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The pursuit logic had switched to <em>containment mode</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "The exits are getting sealed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "I know. Elias needs more time.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "You're sure he can do it?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She didn't answer. Instead, she used her body's center of gravity to redirect an approaching soldier's trajectory, creating the space for Soren's cannon to find an angle.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "Cover me. I'm going to buy Elias time.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She didn't wait for Soren's response. She walked straight into the center of the hall.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She didn't try to defeat any of the soldiers. She simply made herself the most visible target—wide movements, active engagement, drawing all the remaining soldiers' targeting priority to herself.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She moved between them using only the kind of instinct honed through high-pressure situations, judging every repositioning's timing with precision.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 300,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 6
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Impact on the frame, arm.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 300,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 7
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Another impact, side.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She stumbled backward a step, regained her footing, continued moving.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Sector B shield node ── <em>breach complete</em>",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "Done—shield node, Sector B. The opening won't last long, I can't extend it any further.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "That's enough. Everyone, <em>move now</em>.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "All four sprinted toward the building's north exit simultaneously. Soren released the last of his output in a buffer blast between them and the pursuing soldiers.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 400,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 8
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Lyra pushed open the safety door. Before them stretched the Ark's outer perimeter—open, empty wasteland.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The shield's Sector B was directly ahead. The luminous barrier already showed an irregular opening, its edges trembling slightly—like a wound about to heal.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "They ran for it.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "glitch",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "noise",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Crossing the shield created a faint electrical sensation, a current-like feeling that penetrated the skin and left a brief tingling in the nerve endings.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Then it was gone.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "noise",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "All four landed on the other side of the shield.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Elias glanced back. The opening had already sealed, the shield whole again. Several artificial soldiers stood at the barrier's edge, sensors sweeping outward, but they didn't advance further.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Crossing the border wasn't within their operational authority. They could only stand on that side of the light barrier.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Four people stood beyond the shield. Outside the Ark's boundary for the first time.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The air here was different from inside the shield, dry and faintly radioactive in a way that rasped against the senses. The wind was stronger, coming from no particular direction, whipping their clothes and hair.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The distant horizon was a dull orange, with the outlines of wasteland ruins barely visible in that discolored haze. No paths, no markers, nothing to indicate which direction to go.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Lyra removed the damaged augmentation module from her shoulder and examined the light bruising on her arm from the overload, then lifted her head to look across the vast, unknown wasteland and took a deep breath.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "The air tastes worse than inside.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "No kidding. Radioactive dust.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "But—<delay ms=\"400\"/>it feels different.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No one contradicted her.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Alea stood at the front, looking out across the land she had never set foot on in fifteen years. The wind tousled her hair, and she didn't bother to fix it. She simply stood there, feeling the ground beneath her feet.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Then she took a step forward.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "Let's go. Find shelter before dark.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The three others fell into step behind her.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1500,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "reward",
    "complete"
  ]
}
